lkogonov1991" id="mwENQ">Volkogonov 1991</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwENU"> </span>173.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEEllman20021163-1164-887" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEEllman20021163-1164-887"><a href="./Joseph_Stalin#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEEllman20021163-1164_887-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEEllman20021163-1164-887" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Joseph_Stalin#CITEREFEllman2002" id="mwENY">Ellman 2002</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwENc"> </span>1163-1164.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931022-888" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931022-888"><a href="./Joseph_Stalin#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931022_888-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931022-888" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Joseph_Stalin#CITEREFGettyRitterspornZemskov1993" id="mwENg">Getty, Rittersporn <span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwENk">&amp;</span> Zemskov 1993</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwENo"> </span>1022.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEEllman20021162-1163-889" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEEllman20021162-1163-889"><a href="./Joseph_Stalin#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEEllman20021162-1163_889-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEEllman20021162-1163-889" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Joseph_Stalin#CITEREFEllman2002" id="mwENs">Ellman 2002</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwENw"> </span>1162-1163.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931024-890" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931024-890"><a href="./Joseph_Stalin#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEGettyRitterspornZemskov19931024_890-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="